<br><br>All
are invited to the 117th FFA monthly interclub Aikido practice on
Saturday, 2011 February 05. This series of joint monthly practice sessions
started in 2000. <br><br><br><span style="text-decoration: underline;"></span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">DETAILS:</span><br><br>MAT CONTRIBUTION: &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br>
PhP100<br><br>DATE AND TIME:<br>
Saturday, 2011 February 05<br>1830 hrs (6:30 p.m.)<br>
<br>THIS MONTH'S HOST:<br>Jitsuyo Bugei Aikido Club <br>
<br>THIS MONTH'S VENUE:<br>Club 650<br>
C-5 Road, Libis, Pasig City*<br><br><br>
ALL REGARDLESS OF ORGANIZATIONAL AFFILIATION ARE WELCOME. For more details, e-mail <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="mailto:macaikido@yahoo.com"><span class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1297244124_0">macaikido@yahoo.com</span></a>&nbsp; or call 890-1976 or 77.<br>
<br><br><span style="text-decoration: underline;">III. * Getting there: STREET DIRECTIONS</span><br>
<br>A) DRIVING YOUR CAR<br><br>
Coming from the south (</font><font style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;" size="2">Makati/The Fort etc),</font><font style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;" size="2"> Club
650 is on the right, one lot beyond Shopwise and several lots before the entrance to Eastwood. Coming from the the north
(UP/Ateneo/Blue Ridge area), take C-5 into Libis area and make a u-turn
a few hundred meters after the Jollibee/Delifrance outlet. There is
ample parking in front.<br><br>B) USING PUBLIC TRANSPORTATION<br>
<br>Club
650 is accessible via the jeeps that traverse C-5. From EDSA, get off
at the Ortigas intersection, take a jeep to the Ortigas-C-5
intersection, get off at C-5 and take a second jeep north towards
Eastwood. Club 650 will be on the right coming from the south (Makati), beside Shopwise and before the entrance to Eastwood.</font><br><small style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><font size="2"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"></span></font></span></small><font size="2"><br style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">
</font> 
